profile: With professional, dedicated plumbing service to all major cities and surrounding areas in Alberta, and with some of the best plumbers in the industry, The Gentlemen Plumbers work hard to exceed your expectations and deliver quality. If you need a plumber, call us today for plumbing or heating issues, leaky sinks and faucets, clogged drains, toilet, bathtub and shower repairs, furnace cleaning and repairs, hot water tanks and tankless hot water heaters, furnace installation and maintenance, trenchless pipe repair, camera sewer inspection, and more! We have local branches in Calgary, Edmonton, Red Deer, Lethbridge, and Medicine Hat, with extended service all over Southern Alberta, including Camrose, Sherwood Park, St. Albert, Airdrie, High River, Crossfield, Carstairs, Olds, Innisfail, Wetaskiwin, Leduc, Lacombe, Okotoks, Nanton, Taber, Cardston, Didsbury, Brooks, Crowsnest Pass, Cochrane, Strathmore, Sundre, Three Hills, Ponoka, Fort Macleod, Pincher Creek, Bowden, Fort Saskatchewan, Chestermere, Sylvan Lake, Spruce Grove, and Stony Plain.

profile:
We pride ourselves in Doing Good electrical work, Giving Back to our customers and the communities we serve and leaving a positive Mark wherever we go!

Our residential electricians have what it takes to put the elegant touches on your home projects. We will take away the stress of reading those confusing light fixture install guides, and make the whole process as easy as flicking the switch.

Our qualified electricians will courteously answer any questions and leave your home as neat as they found it. We provide excellent service for any work required such as: New installations, repairs using new components, replacements and upgrades, system inspection and testing, troubleshooting services and every other neat electronic gizmos that make your home cozy.

Our commercial electricians are well equipped with tools and experience in servicing all your requirements. Whether it is a new construction project or renovations to your existing commercial building, we will be there to make sure your project gets done to your satisfaction.

We provide security using the latest technology, automation, and solutions customized to fit your lifestyle. Whether it is your home or your business, Markon Electric has you covered and secured.
